Chris,

Instead of screwing around tring to figure this one out on your
own--take that starter out, take it to any reputable FLAPs and let them
put it on their current draw starter tester.
This will tell you everthing you wanted to know, and maybe somethings
you don't.

Quick, simple, and at least you'll know where you stand real quick.

Later,

Terry


